SBG Securities Hires Macquarie’s Froneman to Research Platinum Companies

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-06-09T07:40:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/sbg-securities-hires-macquarie-s-froneman-to-research-platinum-companies.html
SBG Securities, Standard Bank Group
Ltd.’s brokerage, said it hired Justin Froneman to research
platinum companies, including Anglo American Platinum Ltd. and
 Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd. (IMP)   Froneman joins SBG Securities from Macquarie First South
Securities, Johannesburg-based SBG Securities said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  